feat: add command history search function
Introduces a script to search command history for specific commands or keywords, improving user access to previously used commands.
Implements verbose logging and handles cases where history file is missing.

feat: add function to remove GitHub workflow runs
Introduces a new PowerShell function that utilizes the GitHub CLI to remove workflow runs from a specified repository. This enhances workflow management by allowing for automated run clean-up.
No Breaking Changes

refactor: improve error handling in GitHub rate limits function
Replace warning message with a more explicit error output and exit code when GitHub CLI is not installed. This enhances user awareness and prevents further execution when prerequisites are not met.
Add verbose logging at the end of the function to aid debugging.

config: update PowerShell execution policies
Adds script execution policy and experimental features to enhance functionality and flexibility of PowerShell settings.

Adds a new Markdown file documenting various useful command-line tools, system shortcuts, Control Panel applets, and utilities available in Windows. This provides a quick reference guide for users to utilize Windows features more effectively.
No related issue references.

Enhances documentation with links to PowerShell configuration and profiles, providing users with more resources for setup and management insights.

section.div:
Chore: Disables WinGet CommandNotFound module
Disables the WinGet CommandNotFound module in PowerShell profiles to prevent potential conflicts or issues. This change also includes updates to profile scripts for improved stability and compatibility.
The following changes were made: - Commented out the import of the Microsoft.WinGet.CommandNotFound module in Microsoft.PowerShell_profile.ps1 and Microsoft.VSCode_profile.ps1. - Renamed `Log-Debug` to `Write-ProfileLog` for clarity and consistency. - Added integration for VSCode shell environment using `code --locate-shell-integration-path pwsh`. - Included Chocolatey module profile import.
